                {
                  "text": "178. Preventive services such as immunization/vaccinations services and other preventive services (e.g., tetanus toxoid for pregnant women, and routine immunization such as BCG during well child visits). Exclude the cost of vaccine itself. \u2014 Consumed...",
                  "language": "EN"
                },
                {
                  "text": "178. Preventive services such as immunization/vaccinations services and other preventive services (e.g., tetanus toxoid for pregnant women, and routine immunization such as BCG during well child visits). Exclude the cost of vaccine itself. \u2014 Consumed...",
